  "slug": "celestial",
  "title": "Celestial",
  "description": "A Minecraft mod for Fabric and Forge that allows you to customize the sky.",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fishcute/Celestial/main/modpage/logo.png\" alt=\"Logo\" width=\"628\" height=\"163\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fishcute/Celestial/main/modpage/line.png\"></p>\n<p><em><a href=\"https://github.com/fishcute/Celestial/wiki\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/sbxmXSa.png\" alt=\"github\" width=\"223\" height=\"75\"></a></em></p>\n<p>Celestial is a mod that allows you to customize the sky in many ways, such as adding new planets, changing stars, and many other things! Everything is configured through a resource pack, so there is no need to mess through configs. Celestial also supports a wide variety of versions, with resource packs functioning identical on each different version.</p>\n<h2><strong><img src=\"https://github.com/fishcute/Celestial/blob/main/modpage/features_banner.png?raw=true\" alt=\"features\" width=\"600\" height=\"72\"><br></strong></h2>\n<p>- The creation of new planets and stars in the sky.</p>\n<p>- Customization of the sky and fog colors.</p>\n<p>- Customization of the fog distance.</p>\n<p>- The ability to change the color and height of clouds.</p>\n<p>- The creation of sky boxes with custom textures or solid colors.</p>\n<p>- The ability to create immersive and animated skies, with countless variables available for use.</p>\n<p>- Being able to customize the sky of any vanilla or modded dimension.</p>\n<p>- And much more!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fishcute/Celestial/main/modpage/note.png\" alt=\"Without any resource packs, this mod will not affect anything\" width=\"1036\" height=\"57\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/fishcute/Celestial/main/modpage/line.png\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/fishcute/Celestial/blob/main/modpage/demo_banner.png?raw=true\" alt=\"demo\" width=\"600\" height=\"72\"></p>\n<p>Below are a few examples of what Celestial is capable of.</p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><strong><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/661111/description_be97793d-707e-4689-bbfc-a7ec3663dd97.png\"></strong></p>\n<p><strong>An alien planet sky.</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZZIWRqQ.png\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\"></p>\n<p><strong><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/661111/description_5c1aec64-4f78-41dd-a290-7fdd159cfd3f.png\"></strong></p>\n<p><strong>The Overworld, rendering at y = 11,000.</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/urFmIz4.png\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\"></p>\n<p><strong><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/661111/description_b8aa9211-e7c9-440b-a3cb-376764ce1c8d.png\"></strong></p>\n<p><strong>A hurricane.</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/GSkrvvD.png\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/661111/description_0df2cd3a-37b8-47e4-b3ff-4e26e6e870a0.png\"></p>\n<p><strong>A night sky with planets from the Solar System.</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/w4j40K9.png\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/661111/description_de9bdd82-d5ee-421f-b46a-4af3eefa267b.png\"></p>\n<p><strong>Moons (Not available as a demo).</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/t2Gx3bP.png\" width=\"775\" height=\"400\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/661111/description_63a06273-fcdb-401f-8cc0-1dfbbab11671.png\"></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h3>Want to try out these demos? Download them&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/celestial-demo-packs\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a></h3>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/fishcute/Celestial/blob/main/modpage/line.png?raw=true\" alt=\"line.png\"></p>\n<h2><strong>Check out these resource packs with Celestial support made by UsernameGeri!</strong></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/hyper-realistic-sky\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Hyper Realistic Sky</strong> - Adds an extremely realistic skybox to the sky.</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"/linkout?remoteUrl=https%253a%252f%252fcdn.modrinth.com%252fdata%252fPsMUgCo5%252f9dfcd16ad30862485e9ca2b9857327bc7fbb1999_96.webp\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/PsMUgCo5/9dfcd16ad30862485e9ca2b9857327bc7fbb1999_96.webp\"></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/snowy-mountains-sky\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Snowy Mountains Sky</strong> - Adds realistic mountain ranges to your Minecraft worlds.</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/B9RvpVrv/471d554c89ca16d6248aac4a618beba433b921b5_96.webp\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/elden-ring-sky\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Elden Ring Sky</strong> - Adds several skyboxes from Elden Ring.</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/661111/description_9c74a6de-1976-442e-9a80-45b7c7ab2984.webp\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/fishcute/Celestial/blob/main/modpage/line.png?raw=true\" alt=\"line.png\"></p>\n<p><strong>Fabric versions require <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fabric-api\" rel=\"nofollow\">Fabric API</a></strong></p>\n<p>If you are interested in making your own resource pack, check out the wiki <a href=\"https://github.com/fishcute/Celestial/wiki\" rel=\"nofollow\">here</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Feel free to use this in modpacks or personal content!</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/fishcute/Celestial/blob/main/modpage/line.png?raw=true\" alt=\"line.png\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Need assistance with anything, or having issues? Join the discord!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://discord.gg/9KsHkDE6u2\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/eQQ9rTs.png\" width=\"310\" height=\"100\"></a></p>",
